- Moving in with your son's rape victim.

06:00.486 --> 06:03.364
- For God's sake, it's not right.
- I'm not moving in with her.

06:03.448 --> 06:05.158
We're in the same building complex.

06:05.241 --> 06:08.786
- No. This...
- And by the way, I'm not as convinced

06:08.870 --> 06:11.622
as you are, perhaps,
that she was a rape victim.

06:11.706 --> 06:13.541
Oh, my God. I can't...

