06:23.843 --> 06:25.136
What's that supposed to mean?

06:25.219 --> 06:27.472
How many other women did he go to?

06:27.555 --> 06:28.973
If there's one...

06:30.183 --> 06:31.726
there are others.

06:33.269 --> 06:35.146
Oh, my God.

06:35.229 --> 06:36.606
Oh, my God, I'm sorry.

06:36.689 --> 06:38.983
- No, no, no.
- I shouldn't have done that. I...

06:39.067 --> 06:40.318
What shall we call that?

06:42.153 --> 06:43.196
Foreplay?

06:44.363 --> 06:45.364
Grandma.

06:45.448 --> 06:46.949
Oh, dear.

07:01.964 --> 07:05.093
