07:29.325 --> 07:30.325
Um...

07:33.287 --> 07:36.207
There's never any middle ground with you.

07:36.290 --> 07:40.711
Like, when you're upset, it's charge.
Full speed ahead.

07:42.296 --> 07:44.507
If there's a problem, charge.

07:47.844 --> 07:51.264
If there was a problem with us,
where was the charge?

07:52.390 --> 07:55.685
