like you go at everyone else?

07:57.145 --> 08:01.566
There wasn't a problem with us, Ed.
There's a problem with me.

08:29.844 --> 08:31.179
Okay.

08:31.262 --> 08:34.097
Oh, and it is a disco party, so...

08:34.182 --> 08:37.143
And costumes may
or may not be required.

08:37.226 --> 08:40.270
