09:43.960 --> 09:45.711
Grief.

09:45.795 --> 09:47.004
It's...

09:51.092 --> 09:52.635
insurmountable.

09:54.637 --> 09:57.390
Too difficult a battle to be waged alone.

10:00.935 --> 10:02.436
Which is what you had to do.

10:03.562 --> 10:06.065
You were alone after the accident.

10:06.148 --> 10:07.483
Your husband left.

10:09.860 --> 10:11.529
Perry told me.

10:11.612 --> 10:14.532
Yes, he blamed me.

10:15.950 --> 10:16.950
And he left.

10:18.077 --> 10:20.204
And I deserved the blame.

10:20.288 --> 10:21.998
To be left.

10:22.081 --> 10:23.291
You know, Ray...

10:25.084 --> 10:26.127
made a new life.

10:26.210 --> 10:28.546
He got a new family.

10:28.629 --> 10:31.465
He became a devoted father, so I'm told.

10:31.549 --> 10:33.342
It's... It's good.

10:33.426 --> 10:36.429
