11:28.481 --> 11:29.690
Me. Of course.

11:29.774 --> 11:31.150
Uh...

11:31.233 --> 11:32.818
I don't... I don't understand.

11:33.944 --> 11:35.196
The door's hinged.

11:37.782 --> 11:40.534
