13:09.957 --> 13:11.959
Any other legal actions pending?

13:12.042 --> 13:13.252
Uh, right to sue?

13:13.335 --> 13:16.464
- Any punitive judgments in your favor?
- No, sir.

13:16.547 --> 13:19.049
