13:56.837 --> 13:57.838
Medical.

13:59.256 --> 14:01.842
- Did you submit to insurance?
- No.

14:01.926 --> 14:02.926
Why not?

14:03.886 --> 14:05.930
Because it's...

14:06.013 --> 14:08.933
