14:23.405 --> 14:25.282
And I can deny your petition.

14:29.119 --> 14:30.119
Renata...

14:35.626 --> 14:38.671
From dealing with men like you
all my life. Okay?

14:42.299 --> 14:43.299
Mm-hm.

14:45.970 --> 14:47.638
