- Are you kidding?

14:57.314 --> 15:00.150
- John, come on.
- It doesn't include that either.

15:00.234 --> 15:03.237
- That's my wedding ring.
- It's not listed.

15:07.366 --> 15:08.366
I'm... I'm not...

15:09.785 --> 15:12.413
- giving my...
- I will handle this later.

15:26.302 --> 15:27.595
We done here?

15:28.554 --> 15:31.849
- How did you get here today?
- We drove.

15:31.932 --> 15:33.267
Personal car?

15:34.476 --> 15:35.894
Tesla, 2017.

15:36.645 --> 15:39.565
- At least we got your ring back.
