that you will pay for this, Gordon.

15:47.114 --> 15:50.367
But today is not that day.

15:50.451 --> 15:53.829
Today is Amabella's day,

15:53.912 --> 15:58.250
and it will be filled with laughter

15:58.334 --> 16:00.586
and magic

16:00.669 --> 16:04.423
and pure, unmitigated joy.

16:17.853 --> 16:20.648
- Hi!
- Welcome to Club Amabella!

16:21.690 --> 16:24.234
- You look incredible. You look...
- Oh, thank you.

16:24.318 --> 16:27.571
- This is my mom, Elizabeth. This is Renata.
- Elizabeth! Renata.

16:27.655 --> 16:29.698
- We have never met.
- No, we have not.

16:29.782 --> 16:32.451
It's such a pleasure,
and thank you so much for inviting me.

16:32.534 --> 16:34.078
Of course.

16:34.161 --> 16:35.954
I mean, The Trammps?

16:36.038 --> 16:37.623
And they're headlining.

16:37.706 --> 16:40.668
- So amazing.
- Come in. Get champagne.

16:40.751 --> 16:42.836
Hi.

16:42.920 --> 16:44.880
Have a wonderful time.

16:44.963 --> 16:47.049
Ziggy Stardust, ladies and gentlemen.

16:47.132 --> 16:50.344
- This is Corey Brockfield.
- I've heard so much about you.

16:50.427 --> 16:53.847
