Welcome to my home.

16:53.931 --> 16:55.974
- No, hi. Bonnie.
- Hi.

16:56.058 --> 16:58.811
- Nice to meet you.
- Gordon. Get him some champagne.

16:58.894 --> 17:00.854
I can't. He's so cute,
I can't even take it.

17:00.938 --> 17:03.065
- I can't. I can't. I can't.
- Just don't tell him.

17:03.148 --> 17:04.400
- Get on that.
- He's so cute.

17:04.483 --> 17:06.026
You guys have to be cool.

17:06.109 --> 17:08.612
- I made the biggest mistake bringing him.
- I'm never cool.

17:08.695 --> 17:10.321
