for mature couples.

18:11.175 --> 18:13.552
- Yeah, right.
- Maybe it used to be a...

18:13.635 --> 18:17.139
Celeste, what exactly
does your mother-in-law know?

18:17.222 --> 18:19.933
She gave me a very strange look yesterday.

18:20.017 --> 18:22.519
